(17755, 4477, 0, 1, 'She', '內心的掙扎，好似天使與惡魔的化身一般。看似正確的選擇，卻不一定是好的。說服自己放棄了夢想、企圖，剩下的只會是無盡的後悔與嘆息。何不趁著現在還殘留著孩提時的不顧一切的勇氣，掙脫束縛，作個被夢想惡魔綁架的靈魂。', '2009-05-25 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'Looks like an angle\nShe with film less soul and perfect smile\nDon''t you see what behind her eyes?\nThere just the evil sigh you never know\nShe says “no no no ~ you don’t have to try just to be a normal”\nBut you get in doubt, you should know\nShe just want control you all\n\nDon’t you see what behind her smile?\nJust to do what you always know\n\nDon’t look back she’s always be there\nLike the shadow never go away\nJust do it or regret whole life\nYou must run \nRun away\n\n\nShe has a greedy soul\nYou better careful\nShe looks like an angle\nYou better careful\n\nDon’t you see what under her smile?\nYou should do what you always know\n\nDon’t look back she’s always be there\nLike the shadow never go away\nJust do it or regret whole life\nYou must run\nRun away\nDon’t look back she’s always be there\nLike the shadow never go away\nDon’t be silly to compromise\nYou must go \nGo away', '', 266, '', '恰吉', '恰吉', 'SdbS', 'SdbS', '', 1, 0, 0, '2009-06-05 13:37:31', '2015-03-12 13:39:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
